greediness to a whole new level.} Kxf7 8. Be3 $2 {As often happens in this
variation, a seemingly natural developing move for White can equal an
immediate loss.} Bb4+ 9. Kf2 (9. Nc3 {is best, but still losing:} Re8 10. Kf2 (
