is faced with an unpleasant choice.} 14. Bb3 ({After} 14. g4 Bg6 15. Bb3 (15.
b3 Bb4 16. Bd2 Ba3 $1 {is awkward to deal with}) 15... Bd3 16. Bxc7 Nxc4 17.
