15. Nb3 Nxg2+ 16. Kf1 Bh3 17. Nfd4 Bxc5 18. Bg4+ Bxg4 19. Kxg2 Bxd4 20. Nxd4
Rxd4 {and Black has a crushing advantage, Cl.Dubois-R.Tleptsok, correspondence
